SMART SORT  
This is a project that will help you to make garbage sorting more convenient and faster.  
Are you ready to join us to create a better future?  
A project by Rain-Ba | MDDN201  
WHY ?  
We all know that New Zealand announced the ban on the use of plastic bags nationwide on July  
1
this year. I wasn't mainly accustomed to the beginning, and I needed to have a shopping bag  
that I could use many times. At that time, my understanding of environmental protection was not  
deep enough. Until I saw a public service advertisement in Thailand and some national geographic  
reports, I realized the impact of plastic bags on our environment and the entire ecology.  
Environmental protection is a global issue and a problem we face every day. The most basic thing  
to do is waste sorting. This year, we implemented a waste sorting policy in Shanghai, China. From  
children to the elderly, we must learn to classify garbage.  
Reference:  
https://www.nationalgeographic.com/news/2014/4/140414-ocean-  
garbage-patch-plastic-paciﬁc-debris/  
https://wellington.govt.nz/services/environment-and-waste/rubbish-  
and-recycling/recycling  
https://www.recycle.co.nz/easytodo.php  
http://www.reclaim.co.nz/duties.php  
AIMS  
We are now developing more and more rapidly, and we are facing more and more problems.  
Environmental protection is the most critical issue for everyone. However, how many people  
know how to classify garbage? I hope to make an app to help more people solve this problem  
and also contribute to the green world. The purpose of this app is to give users a comprehensive  
understanding of spam classiﬁcation and to categorize it consciously. At the same time, it can  
encourage more people to join the green action, which will set the point reward. This reward  
mechanism is provided based on the user uploading photos and answering the corresponding  
questions. We need a joint effort for a better future.  
AUDIENCE  
This software is for anyone, because any of us are producing garbage at any time, so this software  
is for everyone. Parents can use this software to teach children how to classify garbage and  
develop a good habit from childhood. For the elderly, the garbage can be disposed of reasonably,  
and some garbage can be reused, such as fertilizer for planting ﬂowers, etc.  
COLOR CHOOSE  
The colors chosen are mainly warm tones and a  
transition from yellow to orange. Warm colors give  
people a feeling of being warmer and more able to  
distinguish between cool colors that are generally  
environmentally friendly. Adding light blue and light  
green at the same time will not appear too dull.  
#FCE76C #FFD164  
#FFD968 #FCE76C #FF8E74  
#
579FFB #7ADE81  
ICON CHOOSE  
Regarding the choice of the icon, I hope to be  
similar to the overall style. The style of black and  
white pure lines can not reﬂect the effect of the  
image, so I chose the icon with lines and colors  
to make it easier for the user to remember.
